title: Bavarian Landtag Elections
new-page: true
tags: event
priority: -2
view-if: (year = bavaria_election_year and month >= bavaria_election_month) or (year > bavaria_election_year)
on-departure: month_actions += 1; bavaria_election_year = year + 4; bavaria_election_month = month
set-jump: bavarian_landtag_results

= Bavarian Landtag Elections, [+ month : month +] [+ year +]

Bavaria holds Landtag elections. This system reuses the federal party-support system, applies Bavarian party weights, normalizes the result, and allocates **128** Landtag seats with D’Hondt.

- @calculate_bavarian_landtag: Count the votes.

@calculate_bavarian_landtag
on-arrival: bavaria_government = 2 if bavaria_government == undefined; bavaria_leader = "Heinrich Held" if bavaria_leader == undefined; bavaria_majority_cabinet = 1 if bavaria_majority_cabinet == undefined
go-to: election_algorithm
set-jump: bavarian_landtag_results

@bavarian_landtag_results
on-arrival: {! Q.bavaria_next_election_year_preview = (Number(Q.year) || 0) + 4; Q.bavaria_next_election_month_preview = Q.month; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.calculateBavarianLandtagResults === 'function') { window.calculateBavarianLandtagResults(Q); } !}

= Bavarian Landtag election results

Next Bavarian election after this Landtag is due in **[+ bavaria_next_election_month_preview : month +] [+ bavaria_next_election_year_preview +]**.

Bavarian Landtag seats: **[+ bavaria_landtag_total_seats +] / 128**

Current Bavarian government: **[+ bavaria_current_government_name +]** ([+ bavaria_current_government_parties +]) led by **[+ bavaria_leader +]**.

Current government seats: **[+ bavaria_current_government_seats +] / 128**. Status: **[+ bavaria_current_government_status +]**. Majority cabinet: **[+ bavaria_majority_cabinet +]**.

Current government leverage: **[+ bavaria_leverage +]**.

