{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#8B0000'> </div> !} KPD{!</td><td>!} [+ bavaria_kpd_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ bavaria_kpd_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#000'> </div> !} BVP/Z{!</td><td>!} [+ bavaria_bvp_z_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ bavaria_bvp_z_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#DCCA4A'> </div> !} [+ ddp_name +]{!</td><td>!} [+ bavaria_ddp_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ bavaria_ddp_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#D5AC27'> </div> !} DVP{!</td><td>!} [+ bavaria_dvp_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ bavaria_dvp_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#3f7bc1'> </div> !} DNVP{!</td><td>!} [+ bavaria_dnvp_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ bavaria_dnvp_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#954B00'> </div> !} NSDAP{!</td><td>!} [+ bavaria_nsdap_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ bavaria_nsdap_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#5E8C31'> </div> !} Bavarian Peasant Party{!</td><td>!} [+ bavaria_peasant_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ bavaria_peasant_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#a0a0a0'> </div> !} Others{!</td><td>!} [+ bavaria_other_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ bavaria_other_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!</table>!}

= Choose a Bavarian coalition

A coalition is selectable if it controls at least **65** of the **128** Landtag seats. If no listed coalition has a majority, the incumbent Bavarian government may continue as a minority cabinet.

- @bavaria_select_traffic_light
- @bavaria_select_bvp_peasant_dnvp
- @bavaria_select_bvp_dnvp
- @bavaria_select_bvp_ddp_peasant
- @new_bavarian_elections: Call new Bavarian Landtag elections.
- @root: Continue without changing the Bavarian government.

@bavaria_select_traffic_light
title: Traffic Light
subtitle: DDP + Peasant + SPD — [+ bavaria_traffic_light_coalition_seats +] / 128 — [+ bavaria_traffic_light_coalition_status +]
view-if: bavaria_traffic_light_coalition_selectable = 1
on-arrival: {! Q.bavaria_government = 1; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.updateBavarianCoalitionOptions === 'function') { window.updateBavarianCoalitionOptions(Q); } !}
go-to: bavaria_leader_selection

@bavaria_select_bvp_peasant_dnvp
title: BVP-Peasant-DNVP
subtitle: BVP/Z + Peasant + DNVP — [+ bavaria_bvp_peasant_dnvp_coalition_seats +] / 128 — [+ bavaria_bvp_peasant_dnvp_coalition_status +]
view-if: bavaria_bvp_peasant_dnvp_coalition_selectable = 1
on-arrival: {! Q.bavaria_government = 2; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.updateBavarianCoalitionOptions === 'function') { window.updateBavarianCoalitionOptions(Q); } !}
go-to: bavaria_leader_selection

@bavaria_select_bvp_dnvp
title: BVP-DNVP
subtitle: BVP/Z + DNVP — [+ bavaria_bvp_dnvp_coalition_seats +] / 128 — [+ bavaria_bvp_dnvp_coalition_status +]
view-if: bavaria_bvp_dnvp_coalition_selectable = 1
on-arrival: {! Q.bavaria_government = 3; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.updateBavarianCoalitionOptions === 'function') { window.updateBavarianCoalitionOptions(Q); } !}
go-to: bavaria_leader_selection

@bavaria_select_bvp_ddp_peasant
title: BVP-DDP-Peasant
subtitle: BVP/Z + DDP + Peasant — [+ bavaria_bvp_ddp_peasant_coalition_seats +] / 128 — [+ bavaria_bvp_ddp_peasant_coalition_status +]
view-if: bavaria_bvp_ddp_peasant_coalition_selectable = 1
on-arrival: {! Q.bavaria_government = 4; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.updateBavarianCoalitionOptions === 'function') { window.updateBavarianCoalitionOptions(Q); } !}
go-to: bavaria_leader_selection

@new_bavarian_elections
title: Call new Bavarian Landtag elections.
on-arrival: bavaria_election_year = year; bavaria_election_month = month
go-to: calculate_bavarian_landtag

@bavaria_leader_selection

= Choose the Bavarian leader

Selected coalition: **[+ bavaria_current_government_name +]** ([+ bavaria_current_government_parties +]).

Coalition seats: **[+ bavaria_current_government_seats +] / 128**. Status: **[+ bavaria_current_government_status +]**.

- @bavaria_leader_vogel
- @bavaria_leader_held

@bavaria_leader_vogel
title: Kurt Vogel
subtitle: Available because the SPD is in the Bavarian cabinet.
view-if: bavaria_government = 1
on-arrival: bavaria_leader = "Kurt Vogel"
go-to: bavarian_government_confirmed

@bavaria_leader_held
title: Heinrich Held
subtitle: Available because BVP/Z is in the Bavarian cabinet.
view-if: bavaria_government = 2 or bavaria_government = 3 or bavaria_government = 4
on-arrival: bavaria_leader = "Heinrich Held"
go-to: bavarian_government_confirmed

@bavarian_government_confirmed

= Bavarian government formed

Coalition: **[+ bavaria_current_government_name +]**

Parties: **[+ bavaria_current_government_parties +]**

Seats: **[+ bavaria_current_government_seats +] / 128**

Status: **[+ bavaria_current_government_status +]**

Leader: **[+ bavaria_leader +]**

Next Bavarian election: **[+ bavaria_next_election_year_preview +]**, in **[+ bavaria_next_election_month_preview : month +]**.

- @root: Continue.
